file.name: object_without_fields_reference.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  version: 1.0.0
  title: World Bank Indicator API
  description: Here you can find documentation for COVID-19 REST API.
servers:
  - description: Indicators represent data like total population, gross national income, energy use, and many more
    url: http://api.worldbank.org/v2/
paths:
  /country/{country_name}/indicator/NY.GDP.MKTP.CD:
    get:
      tags: ["GDP data of a given country"]
      operationId: getGDPBycountry
      parameters:
        - name: date
          in: query
          description: Date-range by year, month or quarter that scopes the result-set.
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: country_name
          in: path
          description: Date-range by year, month or quarter that scopes the result-set.
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: format
          in: query
          description: Format of the response.
          required: false
          schema:
            type: string
            default: json
      responses:
        '200':
          description: List GDP information of each year
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items: {}
components:
  schemas:
    Country:
      type: object
      properties:
        id:
          type: string
          example: CHL
        value:
          type: string
          example: Chilie
    YouthLiteracyRate:
      type: object
      properties:
        indicator:
          type: object
        country:
          "$ref": "#/components/schemas/Country"
        date:
          type: string
          example: "2016"
        value:
          type: integer
          example: 100
        decimal:
          type: integer
          example: 2
    Error:
      type: object
      properties:
        name:
          type: string
